snippet.title: Johnny Depp: Ex-partner Winona Ryder tells High Court he was ‘never violent’ | 5 News
snippet.description:
► Subscribe to 5 News: http://bit.ly/5NewsSub 

► Johnny Depp's ex-partner Winona Ryder has said it's "impossible to believe" allegations from his former wife that he was violent. 

She provided a written statement to the High Court, calling Mr Depp a 'really good man'. 

Mr Depp is suing the Sun newspaper over an article that called him a 'wife-beater' which they say is accurate and he denies.

►Johnny Depp libel trial: actor denies repeatedly slapping Amber Heard
